    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know what people say about therapy and healing, but it just feels like a lot of noise. it doesn't change the fact that the person i was meant to be is gone. it's like being a tombstone for a life that never happened. honestly, it feels more like an act of mercy to just stop pretending. why keep dragging this empty shell around when it has nothing left to offer the world?",
